Good hygiene, acceptable price, Chinese restaurant with food and dim-sum cooked in 'fastfood' taste

This place has the worst hygiene. The spoon that they have me still had bread crumbs stuck to it. And the table cloth had black stuff on it so they turn it around and they didn't care that there was even more black stuff on it. Don't even get me started on their teacups and bowls. I wonder if they actually clean the bowls...
the dim sum not upto standard .

reviews.text: It's clean and well lit. There are many useful shops like 360 and JHC. The restaurants have good food at very reasonable prices.

Trendy place with ample eating food stores  within  this little part of Tuen Mun. There are also shops like sago rice milk tea, grooming and spa, supermarket, pharmacy and Traditional Chinese Medicine doctors, boutiques, banks, fancy cakes and bakeries, etc.
A good shopping centre with full of shops and exhibition displays. A must visit!
Small but great shopping mall.
A good place of waiting for the ferry arrival.

result.adr_address: 香港屯門湖翠路168-236號
result.name: 稻香

reviews.text: 酒樓做下午茶點心半價,但雷聲大,雨點小。貨不對辦!虾餃皮厚肉少,㹓賣蒸到缩晒水。難食過「飽點」昨曰才喺旺角稻香食完,真喺差天共地
主要價錢平，早茶下午茶半價。
來食過好多次，今餐叫咗半隻燒鵝，上枱時變咗燒鵝+燒鴨唔好搵人老襯
飲下午茶，交通方便，設有停车场，还有泊车優惠，食品方便算ok，價錢不贵、款式都多，只是仕應不足夠
點心一般 ，不過好招呼過碼頭嗰間聯邦 ，聯邦 嗰啲夥記嘅招呼唔好， 落咗單 45分鐘 ，追佢先知冇落單，嗰啲夥記又負氣，招呼唔好， 從未見過有間酒樓啲夥記 咁衰
